headline: A 12-Year-Old’s Journey Into the World of Ozempic
summary: A mother found success with a weight-loss drug after a lifelong battle. Noticing her young daughter start down the same path, she decided to have her try semaglutide, the active ingredient in Wegovy and Ozempic.
